comments.body:
When invoking `bundle install`, I am repeatedly encountering errors to the effect of the following:

```bash
An error occurred while installing libv8 (3.16.14.19), and Bundler cannot continue.
Make sure that `gem install libv8 -v '3.16.14.19' --source 'https://rubygems.org/'` succeeds before bundling.

In Gemfile:
  therubyracer was resolved to 0.12.3, which depends on
    libv8
```

This may simply be related to the C compilation tools which are used by default within the macOS Big Sur release 11.2.3 environment.
Reopening until prod is provisioned with the right node version.
